text: The Millennium Democratic Party (Partido Milénio Democrático) is a political party in East Timor. In the parliamentary election held on 30 June 2007, the party won 0.69% of the total votes and did not win any seats in parliament, as it did not reach the 3% threshold to win seats."National Provisional Results from the 30 June 2007 Parliamentary Elections", Comissão Nacional de Eleições Timor-Leste, 9 July 2007. ==References== Category:Political parties in East Timor
title: Millennium Democratic Party (East Timor)
